data.title: Stretford, England, United Kingdom
data.text:
Stretford is a town in Greater Manchester, England, located about 5 miles southwest of Manchester city centre. The town has a population of around 40,000 people and is known for its rich industrial heritage, particularly in the textile and engineering industries. The weather in Stretford is typically mild and temperate, with average temperatures ranging from 4°C in January to 18°C in July.
